<!--
  Compass Rose icon foreground for adaptive icon.
  A clean 4-pointed star / compass rose with N marked in orange-red.
  N arm (top) is longer — in BrightOrangeRed (#FF4500).
  S arm (bottom) is medium — in white.
  E + W arms are shorter — in soft lavender.
  No watch details, no glass, no metal texture.
-->
